#References- https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs

- sudo yum install -y yum-utils
- sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo
- sudo yum -y install terraform

- mkdir terra
- vi main.tf
  Paste all the content which is there in main.tf outside
- vi compute.tf
  Paste all the content which is there in compute.tf outside
- vi variables.tf
  Paste all the content which is there in variables.tf outside

- terraform init
- terraform plan
- terraform apply
- terraform destroy

